<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dōu yǒu zǒu lù de jiān nán 迦南412</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dōu yǒu zǒu lù de jiān nán dōu kǔ guò nǐ de kǔ;
 yōu shāng guò nǐ de yōu shāng máng lù guò nǐ de máng lù;
 tài yáng qiān zhe de qiú shù gēn qiān zhe ní tǔ;
 duì fāng qiān zhe duì fāng shǒu qiān shǒu yī qǐ zǒu;
 chèn de hái cún liú; jià sè zhòu yè hán shǔ;
 yé sū shuō nǐ yào zhōng xīn zǒu wán nǐ gāi zǒu de lù;
 chèn de hái cún liú; jià sè zhòu yè hán shǔ;
 yé sū shuō nǐ yào zhōng xīn zǒu wán nǐ gāi zǒu de lù;</lyrics>
<hymn_number>412</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>